ormal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當你諗到要保持正能量嗰陣，你已經失去正能量<br />\n出下街，做下運動，睇下書，就算未搵到工，至少會覺得自己做緊啲嘢係有得著，你會覺得充實啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c066507bf41e4b7cbd7dc3eedd904b28d61673d8","tid":653464,"uid":522,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T21:59:27.000Z","msg":"隔一陣就同自己講醒神醒神<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e4085c803abf09bfd86887e9dbdb24f6dc0ef09","tid":653464,"uid":180903,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-05T14:26:04.000Z","msg":"好幸福 今日番下pt 個老細讚我係咁多個pt之中最正常 仲開左個高價比我番 不過我話淨係番得三個月 佢話佢問下班大佬 嗚 好感動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n趁我有力放下正能量先！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}